  "text": "Hi {{first_name}},\n\nthe card ending in {{card_last4}} expires on {{expiry_month}}. Updating it now keeps {{product_name}} active without interruption.\n\nCard ending: {{card_last4}}\nExpires: {{expiry_month}}\nPlan: {{plan_name}}\nNext renewal: {{renewal_date}}\n\nUpdate payment method: {{billing_url}}\n\nFor security, we never include full card numbers in email.",
  "mjml": "<mjml>\n  <mj-head>\n    <mj-title>Payment Method Expiring</mj-title>\n    <mj-preview>A proactive billing email with urgency, but without alarmist copy.</mj-preview>\n    <mj-attributes>\n      <mj-all font-family=\"-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif\" />\n      <mj-text color=\"#1f1215\" font-size=\"16px\" line-height=\"24px\" />\n      <mj-section padding=\"0\" />\n      <mj-button border-radius=\"999px\" font-size=\"15px\" font-weight=\"800\" inner-padding=\"15px 24px\" />\n    </mj-attributes>\n  </mj-head>\n  <mj-body background-color=\"#fff1f2\" width=\"600px\">\n    <mj-section padding=\"28px 22px 14px\">\n      <mj-column>\n        <mj-text align=\"center\" color=\"#6d555b\" font-size=\"12px\" font-weight=\"800\" letter-spacing=\"1.8px\" text-transform=\"uppercase\">{{product_name}}</mj-text>\n      </mj-column>\n    </mj-section>\n    <mj-section background-color=\"#2a0d12\" border-radius=\"22px 22px 0 0\" padding=\"34px 34px 28px\">\n      <mj-column>\n        <mj-text color=\"#f43f5e\" font-size=\"11px\" font-weight=\"900\" letter-spacing=\"2px\" text-transform=\"uppercase\" padding=\"0 0 14px\">Payment method</mj-text>\n        <mj-text color=\"#fff7f8\" font-size=\"30px\" font-weight=\"850\" line-height=\"36px\" padding=\"0 0 12px\">Update your card before the next renewal</mj-text>\n        <mj-text color=\"#fff7f8\" font-size=\"15px\" line-height=\"24px\" padding=\"0\">Hi {{first_name}}, the card ending in {{card_last4}} expires on {{expiry_month}}. Updating it now keeps {{product_name}} active without interruption.</mj-text>\n      </mj-column>\n    </mj-section>\n    <mj-section background-color=\"#ffffff\" border-radius=\"0 0 22px 22px\" padding=\"0 30px 30px\">\n      <mj-column>\n        <mj-spacer height=\"26px\" />\n        <mj-text background-color=\"#ffe4e6\" color=\"#1f1215\" font-size=\"13px\" font-weight=\"800\" line-height=\"20px\" padding=\"18px 20px 4px\">Card ending</mj-text>\n        <mj-text background-color=\"#ffe4e6\" color=\"#1f1215\" font-size=\"28px\" font-weight=\"900\" line-height=\"34px\" padding=\"0 20px 18px\">{{card_last4}}</mj-text>\n        <mj-table padding=\"22px 0 4px\">\n          <tr><td style=\"padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #fecdd3;color:#6d555b;font-size:13px;\">Expires</td><td align=\"right\" style=\"padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #fecdd3;color:#1f1215;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;\">{{expiry_month}}</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #fecdd3;color:#6d555b;font-size:13px;\">Plan</td><td align=\"right\" style=\"padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #fecdd3;color:#1f1215;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;\">{{plan_name}}</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #fecdd3;color:#6d555b;font-size:13px;\">Next renewal</td><td align=\"right\" style=\"padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #fecdd3;color:#1f1215;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;\">{{renewal_date}}</td></tr>\n        </mj-table>\n        <mj-button href=\"{{billing_url}}\" background-color=\"#f43f5e\" color=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"26px 0 8px\">Update payment method</mj-button>\n        <mj-text align=\"center\" color=\"#6d555b\" font-size=\"13px\" line-height=\"20px\" padding=\"18px 10px 0\">For security, we never include full card numbers in email.</mj-text>\n      </mj-column>\n    </mj-section>\n    <mj-section padding=\"22px 20px 40px\">\n      <mj-column>\n        <mj-text align=\"center\" color=\"#6d555b\" font-size=\"12px\" line-height=\"18px\">TemplateForge marketplace template. Update branding and URLs before production use.</mj-text>\n      </mj-column>\n    </mj-section>\n  </mj-body>\n</mjml>",
